{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idcc838834-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"60127"},"text":"§ 60127.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Population encroachment and rights-of-way","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idcc838835-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Study","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Transportation, in conjunction with the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission and in consultation with appropriate Federal agencies and State and local governments, shall undertake a study of land use practices, zoning ordinances, and preservation of environmental resources with regard to pipeline rights-of-way and their maintenance.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idcc838836-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Purpose of Study","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The purpose of the study shall be to gather information on land use practices, zoning ordinances, and preservation of environmental resources—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcc838837-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to determine effective practices to limit encroachment on existing pipeline rights-of-way;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcc838838-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to address and prevent the hazards and risks to the public, pipeline workers, and the environment associated with encroachment on pipeline rights-of-way;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcc838839-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to raise the awareness of the risks and hazards of encroachment on pipeline rights-of-way; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcc83883a-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/b/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" to address how to best preserve environmental resources in conjunction with maintaining pipeline rights-of-way, recognizing pipeline operators’ regulatory obligations to maintain rights-of-way and to protect public safety.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idcc83883b-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Considerations","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In conducting the study, the Secretary shall consider, at a minimum, the following:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcc83883c-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The legal authority of Federal agencies and State and local governments in controlling land use and the limitations on such authority.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcc83883d-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The current practices of Federal agencies and State and local governments in addressing land use issues involving a pipeline easement.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcc83883e-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/c/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The most effective way to encourage Federal agencies and State and local governments to monitor and reduce encroachment upon pipeline rights-of-way.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idcc83883f-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Report.—","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcc838840-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"In general","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Not later than 1 year after the date of enactment of this subsection, the Secretary shall publish a report identifying practices, laws, and ordinances that are most successful in addressing issues of encroachment and maintenance on pipeline rights-of-way so as to more effectively protect public safety, pipeline workers, and the environment.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcc838841-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Distribution of report","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall provide a copy of the report to—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idcc838842-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/d/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Congress and appropriate Federal agencies; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idcc838843-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/d/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" States for further distribution to appropriate local authorities.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idcc838844-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s60127/d/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Adoption of practices, laws, and ordinances","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall encourage Federal agencies and State and local governments to adopt and implement appropriate practices, laws, and ordinances, as identified in the report, to address the risks and hazards associated with encroachment upon pipeline rights-of-way and to address the potential methods of preserving environmental resources while maintaining pipeline rights-of-way, consistent with pipeline safety.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idcc838845-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/104/304/s16/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 104–304, § 16(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1996-10-12"},"text":"Oct. 12, 1996","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/110/3803"},"text":"110 Stat. 3803","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/355/s11/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–355, § 11(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-12-17"},"text":"Dec. 17, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/116/2996"},"text":"116 Stat. 2996","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idcc838846-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idcc838847-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idcc838848-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The date of enactment of this subsection, referred to in subsec. (d)(1), is the date of enactment of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/355"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–355","children":[],"tail":", which was approved "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-12-17"},"text":"Dec. 17, 2002","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idcc838849-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2002—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/355"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–355","children":[],"tail":" substituted “Population encroachment and rights-of-way” for “Population encroachment” in section catchline and amended text generally. Prior to amendment, text read as follows:"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(a) ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Land Use Recommendations","children":[],"tail":".—The Secretary of Transportation shall make available to an appropriate official of each State, as determined by the Secretary, the land use recommendations of the special report numbered 219 of the Transportation Research Board, entitled ‘Pipelines and Public Safety’."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(b) ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Evaluation","children":[],"tail":".—The Secretary shall—"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(1) evaluate the recommendations in the report referred to in subsection (a);","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(2) determine to what extent the recommendations are being implemented;","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(3) consider ways to improve the implementation of the recommendations; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(4) consider other initiatives to further improve awareness of local planning and zoning entities regarding issues involved with population encroachment in proximity to the rights-of-way of any interstate gas pipeline facility or interstate hazardous liquid pipeline facility.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
